  [ Marc Haber ]
  * new upstream version 1.9.8p2-1
    * this correctly handles double defined alases (Closes: #985412)
    * improve sudoers.ldap.manpage. Thanks to Dennis Filder and
      Eric Brun (Closes: #981190)
