  * new upstream version, fixes a race condition in sudo's pathname
    validation, which is a security issue (CAN-2005-1993),
    closes: #315115, #315718

 -- Bdale Garbee <bdale@gag.com>  Tue, 28 Jun 2005 15:33:11 -0400

